DINO[22] and MaskDINO[10] models, or the document-understanding focused
DiT[11] and LayoutLMv3[7] models. The DocLayNet dataset was used for ﬁne-

augmentation strategies used by the teams include multi-scale and mosaic meth-
ods, as well as deriving synthetic datasets from DocLayNet. Two of the top ﬁve
teams reported that they include the additional text cell layer provided by Do-
cLayNet and the competition dataset in their approach. No teams stated to
create private ground-truth data that was not derived from DocLayNet.
